lin quan n cc s kin trong mt cu hoc gia cc cu. Thng thng ta s c

Chng 1: Gii thiu bi ton
1.1 t vn
Trong lnh vc nghin cu cc m hnh hc my, cc bi ton phn loi
(classification) ni chung c coi l bi ton kinh in, ng vai tr quan trng
trong cc tc v v qun l v trch rt thng tin. T nhng bi ton nh phn loi
nh, phn loi ging ni n bi ton phn loi spam hay phn loi vn bn ni
chung. Trong mt vn bn ta thng ch n cc s kin din ra trong vn bn.
V khi k li, thut li ta thng tp chung ni v cc s kin . Xut pht t thc
t ny sinh nn cc bi ton nhm xc nh c cc s kin c trong mt vn
bn. Nhm bi ton pht trin tip theo l phn loi v xc nh cc mi quan h
gia cc s kin . Mt trong nhng loi mi quan h l quan h nhn qu. Di
y l mt v d v mt vn bn c cc s kin v cu trc quan h nhn qu gia
chng.

Chng 2: C s l thuyt
Trong chng C s l thuyt ny chng ti s trnh by nhng l thuyt

2.1 Biu din ti liu vi nh dng (CAT-)XML
2.1.1 Ti liu XML
XML [4] - Extensible Markup Language c s dng m t d liu.
Tiu chun XML l mt cch linh hot to ra cc nh dng thng tin v chia s
d liu c cu trc. Tiu chun XML, c khuyn ngh s dng bi World Wide
Web Consortium (W3C). D liu XML c gi l t m t hoc t nh ngha,
c ngha l cu trc ca d liu c nhng vi d liu, do khi nhn c file
d liu XML khng cn phi xy dng trc cu trc lu tr d liu; n c
hiu t ng trong XML.
Phn t c bn ca mt ti liu XML l cc th. Mt phn t c mt th bt
u v mt th kt thc. Tt c cc phn t trong mt ti liu XML c cha
trong mt phn t ngoi cng c gi l phn t gc. XML cng c th h tr
cc phn t lng nhau hoc cc phn t bn trong cc phn t. Kh nng ny cho
php XML h tr cc cu trc phn cp. Tn phn t m t ni dung ca phn t,
v cu trc m t mi quan h gia cc phn t.
Mt ti liu XML c coi l "c nh dng tt" (c ngha l, trnh phn
tch c php XML c th c v hiu c) nu nh dng ca n tun th c t
XML, nu n c nh du ng cch v nu cc phn t c lng nhau ng
cch. XML cng h tr kh nng xc nh cc thuc tnh cho cc phn t v m t
cc c im ca cc phn t trong th bt u ca mt phn t. Di y l mt
v d n gin v ni dung ca mt ti liu XML.
<?xml version="1.0" standalone="yes"?>
<conversation>
<greeting>Hello, world!</greeting>
<response>Stop the planet, I want to get off!</response>
</conversation>
14
2.1.2 Ti liu nh dng (CAT-)XML
(CAT-)XML format l mt tiu chun biu vn bn, k tha t biu din
XML. Cu trc ca mt ti liu theo nh dng (CAT-)XML format gm nhng
thnh phn sau. Th gc Document, trong th gc Document gm cc th con:
token, Markables, Relations.
Th token: trong th token c cc thuc tnh quan trng nh: t_id, sentence,
number gip ta xc nh c t hin ti c id t trong vn bn, t thuc cu no
v v tr ca t trong cu.
Th Markables: trong phn t Markables c cc th con nh:
ACTION_ASPECTUAL, ACTION_CAUSATIVE, ACTION_OCCURRENCE,
gip ta xc nh c t no trong vn bn l t s kin cng nh loi s kin m
t th hin. Ngoi ra, cn c cc th con nh: HUMAN_PART_ORG,
HUMAN_PART_PER, LOC_FAC, TIME_DATE, gip ta xc nh c cc
thng tin v cc t ch ngi, a im, thi gian trong vn bn.
Th Relations: trong phn t c cc th con nh: TLINK, PLOT_LINK gip
ta xc nh cc lin kt c trong vn bn gia cc t. Mt s loi lin kt nh:
CONTAINS, PRECONDITION, FALLING_ACTION, CAUSES, CAUSED_BY,
...
Nh vy, vi vn bn c biu din bng nh dng (CAT-)XML format
ta c c nhng thng tin rt c bn v mi t ca vn bn, n nhng thng tin
su hn v cc loi t, lin kt gia cc t. C th ni y l mt nh dng biu
din vn bn rt tt.
2.2 Mng n-ron
2.2.1 Tng quan kin trc
Mng n-ron (Neural network) ci tn c nhc n rt nhiu trong nhng

lnh vc bi ton khc nhau. Mng n-ron c ly tng t cu trc n-ron
trong h thn kinh ca con ngi.

2.2.3 Biu din t bng word2vec

4

2.2.5 Mng n-ron tch chp th (Graph Convolutional Networks)
Khi nim mng GCN
Mng n-ron thu c nhiu thnh tu trong mt thp k gn y. Tuy
nhin, ban u hu ht cc mng n-ron ch lm vic vi d liu lin tc hay d

c coi l bin th nn tng nht ca mng Graph Neural Networks.

(CNN). Mng CNN thng dng trong cc bi ton lm vic vi d liu nh. Trong
mng CNN cc tng s c mt ma trn c ngha nh mt filter nm bt c
nhng c im trong tng phn ca mt bc nh. V d khi filter trt trn mt

mi, T phn bit c bc nh c phi chp mo hay khng. Thc hin
cng t tng , mng GCN s khm ph cc nt hng xm ca mi nt c
c nhng c trng. Bng cch ny Mng tch chp cho th nm bt c cu
